{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/steampage2.gif?t=1739218113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/Sprite-0002__2_.png?t=1739218113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/Sprite-0003.gif?t=1739218113\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore the graveyards of GHOST GOLFING!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u26f3At the start of each level, the hole is there, lonely, on the other side of the field, and you have a series of pieces that form the path to it. There are windmills, pumpkins, gravestones, mirrors, and even portals! Your challenge? Build the perfect path to guide the ball! And believe me, it won't be easy. One misplaced piece, and the ball could end up rolling off the field or flying straight into the lake!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/Sprite-0001.gif?t=1739218113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc7bThe fun increases with each world! Explore the graveyards: 'Will this curve work here? What if I place a bonfire right before this ice block? Does the pumpkin explode?' Only after setting everything up can you take your shot and hope the ball follows the right path. And when it finally drops into the hole after passing through your crazy creations, the feeling of victory is incredible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/Sprite-0001.png?t=1739218113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf83 <strong>GHOST GOLFING</st